data.description: A beautiful, meticulously maintained home situated in SE Bend's Sundance Meadows. Open-concept floorpan, Gourmet kitchen with granite countertops, Great Room with stone surrounded fireplace, and simulated wood floors. This home enjoys privacy with mature, exquisite landscaping, a Gazebo for entertaining, an easement at the back of the lot which extends the yard by 30 feet, as well as a custom shed for exceptional storage. This quiet neighborhood is walking distance to a variety of shopping, restaurants, parks, and school. A wonderful property to see!
